                    <img src="https://placehold.co/500x600/1E88E5/FFFFFF?text=Jembatan+Interkoneksi" alt="Jembatan" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/80 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300 flex flex-col justify-end p-6">
